administrative building Avriopoint Brno is the new headquarters of the Arch society. Design.
No one could have expected that it is also a mini nursery school with everything - walls of colours, imaginative furniture, toys and a playground miniature on the terrace.
Since October last year, can make the children of employees of Arch. design.
society projets-architectonique Arch. Design. workshops have produced a number of buildings in Brno thought its mini nursery school of business since the start of the building Avriopoint.
It employs about 90 people, especially to children and it was important that women architects and managers can quickly return to work.
With contract of employment decreased time, the school is a proposed bonuses to its employees by Arch. Design in the framework of the social agenda.
Manufacturers and architects have the opportunity to combine a work with the care for the children.
These are employees of Arch. Design. themselves have imagined this nursery school and with the support of the leadership they were able to obtain a grant from the European Union and the Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs.
The mini nursery school is financed by the European Social Fund through the operational programme and the budget in the Czech Republic.
With the availability of financing (2.8 mil. CZK). They were able to purchase equipment and appliances and after two years ensure qualified staff and implementation.
After the allocation of funding (two years) Arch. Design has the obligation after 3 years to operate the mini nursery school on its own funds.
The project lasted a year and society Economy rating has helped ensure the endowment.
The care is provided by a qualified personnel, the day a nurse and a teacher of maternal care for children. children can go to school regardless of age, but they have more than three years.
As is a " mini nursery school " there may be that 5 children at the same time, but in the course of the day there has to be replaced.
The school is flexible according to the needs of parents and children of all employees have the right to use the school without the seniority.
Although agise of an individual care and education, the programme of the mini nursery school is comparable to that for pre-school education.
Children are no play but a quality education is also guaranteed - from beginning to prepare for school benches are taught English.
The class is equipped not only of imaginative toys and games but also a computer that children can use.
The presence of small children in the society creates an environment friendly and positive.
Parents can at any time controlling their child and not have the stress of a delay to collect the children in a school of the place of work.
The parents use their time working the most productive way.
It is not surprising that creates a natural relationship of trust between the employee and the employer.
Arch. Design was included among companies that offer a bonus of choice for the recruitment of new employees and who are friendly to the family and this reinforces the marketing of RH.
