The Americans have a new weapon intelligent "
The US army sent in Afghnistan a new weapon ' intelligent ', known only as the code name XM-25.
The generals believe that this new automatic rifle will influence the conflict there with the Taliban and " will change the game " to their advantage.
The new weapon as a super canon specific
The projectiles are guided by laser with an accuracy of a few metres.
Ammunition special weapons 25 mm developed for the gun and containing an explosive highly breaking, functioned as small grenades.
can plan the munitions in such a way that they explode on contact with the target but also to any of their ballistic trajectory.
can therefore be used against an enemy behind a barrier, a wall or a gap.
It was not protected from above and when he falls over a deadly shrapnel rain, it can incapacitate also.
According to Richard Audette who took part in the development of XM-25, the new rifle is the first infantry weapons which used " intelligent ."
" The soldier used mainly in such a way that it is the target, given a laser beam to determine the distance, gives a clear point of view, that it corrected its referred site and based on the détente.
" Say you have referred to 543 metres.
" When you pressez détente, the weapon is responsible and the distance of 543 metres more or less 1, 2, 3 metres, reported Audette.
