The manufacture of ice is a calculation: if the use of the chick with much of sugar, the amount of sugar should be reduced in the recipe.
An extra sugar is necessary for the lemon ice.
Luciano present a device with which it determines the sugar content of various types of fruit (producers use to measure the degree of Oechsle in the grape must).
