The Taiwanese voters are geared towards a sort of closer links with the continent.
What is Taiwan think of her big brother located on the other side of the Strait?
More than 7.5 million voters are presented on 27 November, 70% of people eligible to elect mayors and councillors in five urban districts, in the framework of what is regarded as a general evaluation of the president, Ma Ying-jeou.
