" Luzhkov is the summit. "
" The FSB, the MVD and the militias are at the second level. "
" Finally, ordinary criminals and corrupt inspectors are at the lowest level. "
" It is an inefficient system in which criminal groups fills a void in some areas where the city does not provide some services. "
The report states that the FSB has the money of the largest companies and that police targeted small.
A source, he said, " that the owners of Moscow understood that it was preferable to obtain the protection of MVD and FSB (rather than organized crime groups), because they have more weapons, more resources and more power than the criminal groups but they are also protected by the law. "
" That is why the protection by criminal gangs is not as high. "
The note said that, although the collection of money is extended, the protection can be uneven; even those who pay are sometimes subject to arrest.
Those who do not pay quickly see their close under a pretext or another.
