" Do it all the more that the Iranians you request not to do so ."
For past attempts to discussions channels, " the silence will not solve nothing ," the Iranians are " masters in delaying tactics ."
Mr. Richier added that the arrest of foreigners is " an Iranian tactic familiar: the taking of hostages for political blackmail ."
announced that the release from jail of Clotilde Reiss (who will speak on 16 August, when it takes refuge in the French Embassy) " will require the payment to the Iranians for a large sum of money " (230 000 bond).
